Package: MODIS
Version: 0.2-34
Date: 23-December-2011
Title: MODIS retrieving and processing Package. Pre-processing functionalities for MODIS grid data.  
Depends: R (>= 2.10), RCurl
Suggests: XML, XMLSchema, SSOAP,raster, mapdata
Author: Matteo Mattiuzzi, Jan Verbesselt, Tomislav Hengl, with contibutions from Anja Klisch.
Maintainer: Matteo Mattiuzzi <matteo.mattiuzzi@boku.ac.at>
Description: MODIS retrieving and processing Package. Downloading, reprojecting, resampling, mosaicing, converting, SDS-extraction, bit-extraction and filtering/smoothing capabilities. Download data from FTP (local processing) or using SSOAP (online processing) via the MODIS webservice. Process data with MRT,GDAL,FWT,SSOAP.
URL: http://modis.r-forge.r-project.org/
License: GPL (>=3)
LazyLoad: yes
